                  </persName> were <hi rend="italic">again</hi> indicted for<rs id="t18580510-558-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18580510-558-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18580510-558-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp> stealing 1 watch, value 2<hi rend="italic">l</hi>.; the property of a man unknown, from his person.</rs>
